{"tid":1658723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【葵涌邨聽日10月17要人】","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T05:19:11.000Z","uid":171244,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0545a8c1a074305a6d9a027ec700099f885cb396","tid":1658723,"uid":171244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"明天五點有葵涌邨社區遊行<br />\n<br />\n事源1:10.1晚有十多名手足於邨內被捕<br />\n<br />\n事源2:今日黑警又喺葵涌邨濫捕<br />\n<br />\n//警方今日於葵涌邨採取拘捕行動，一名37歲報稱地盤工人的男子，涉嫌於9月在網上煽惑他人包圍政府建築物，被警方以涉嫌「煽惑他人作出非法集結」作出拘捕。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191016/60158967?fbclid=IwAR2LWbJ7SbBR-540OiNiZLNeKW9KbdvD3v_dKbilFdf7C4AeBVjZG5qkyFE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F60158967%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2LWbJ7SbBR-540OiNiZLNeKW9KbdvD3v_dKbilFdf7C4AeBVjZG5qkyFE&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=77063986\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191016%2F60158967%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2LWbJ7SbBR-540OiNiZLNeKW9KbdvD3v_dKbilFdf7C4AeBVjZG5qkyFE&h=895cf66e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191016/60158967?fbclid=IwAR2LWbJ7SbBR-540OiNiZLNeKW9KbdvD3v_dKbilFdf7C4AeBVjZG5qkyFE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【行動呼籲：10.17 邨內遊行】<br />\n要求房署出席居民會 交待十月一日事宜<br />\n<br />\n就十月一日大量警員入邨以及進行濫捕，令居民人心惶惶，本處於10月3日晚召開緊急居民會，邀請房屋署、商場管理公司「嘉怡」及屋邨管理公司「九源」出席，房屋署拒絕出席。會議上，不少居民提出疑問，但「嘉怡」及「九源」表示需要再向房署查問才能回覆，房署的缺席，令許多問題不能即時作出澄清。<br />\n<br />\n與會居民希望再有跟進居民會，並要求房署需要出席。本處與居民分別去信要求房署出席第二次居民會，惟房署於居民會當日晚上才明確回覆未能出席。<br />\n<br />\n因此，本處發起社區遊行行動，聯同葵涌邨居民向房署遞信，要求房署出席居民會。<br />\n<br />\n行動詳情<br />\n日期：2019年10月17日（四）<br />\n時間：下午五時<br />\n遊行路線：本處集合--&gt;綠葵樓房署--&gt;葵涌商場--&gt;夏葵樓房署<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我推爆佢!!"},{"pid":"ca5e2c495ee47e78b90f2f0602265739320516c0","tid":1658723,"uid":171244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:57:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a7e22dd39e847ca9ef8463854337738a9ba1640","tid":1658723,"uid":171244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"799a3a1f8fabbac5899fa189e2f9aec9e25d10d9","tid":1658723,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"幫你手推"},{"pid":"0b3e5c015973fec746d21c011430a8bd7c9a3856","tid":1658723,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n順便借位<br />\n屌你老母岑子杰單野我要響國際新聞見到！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658212</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全世界同我落<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#PrayForJimmy</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得寫係ProBeijing Red Thugs 